parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become unable to shift gears, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Transmission cannot go over a certain speed
loss of gears
transmission slipping
transmission oil leaks
transmission catches on fire
high-pitched engine noise
inability to shift into gear
transmission shifter falls through the vehicle floor.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: An airbag system malfunction can cause the airbag light to stay on, indicating a potential safety risk.
symptoms: Airbag light stays on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent stalling issue can cause the vehicle to stall unexpectedly, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls unexpectedly
the engine shuts off without warning
the vehicle is unable to start again for an unknown period.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the crankshaft can cause major engine damage, leading to costly repairs and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The crankshaft twists the crank key
the pulley end of the crankshaft breaks off
the engine suffers major damage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the alternator pulley and belt can cause the battery to drain, leading to engine stalling and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The battery drains
the fan belt fails
the alternator pulley and belt slip
causing battery and belt failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine fires can cause serious damage to the vehicle and potentially harm occupants.
symptoms: The engine catches fire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Oil pressure fluctuations can cause engine damage and potentially lead to engine failure.
symptoms: Oil pressure builds up and drops down.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the window regulators can cause the windows to malfunction, leading to inconvenience and potential safety issues, such as obstructed visibility.
symptoms: Windows do not roll up or down
windows are stuck
windows fall or drop suddenly
windows make unusual noises or vibrations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the defroster/defogger can cause impaired visibility, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Rear window is fogged
defroster does not defrost entire windshield
causes blind spots
impairs driver's vision.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the outside rearview mirror can cause reduced visibility, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Outside rearview mirror does not function
outside rearview mirror is broken or damaged.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield wiper control module can cause a malfunction of the windshield wipers, leading to reduced visibility and potential safety issues.
symptoms: Plastic piece at the end of the windshield wiper control module melted
smoke comes out of the windshield wiper control module
windshield wipers do not function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling can cause loss of power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded, especially when it occurs while driving on the highway.
symptoms: The engine suddenly stops running when coming to a stop or slowing down
and will not restart immediately; the engine will not shut off while idling for hours at a time; the engine restarts hours later.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the neutral safety switch can cause the vehicle to roll or move unexpectedly, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The part is no longer available from the manufacturer; the switch is used to put the vehicle in either park
neutral
or drive.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the engine to stall or not start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Battery failure; alternator failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbag deployment can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of a collision, as the airbag is designed to provide critical protection to the driver and passengers.
symptoms: Airbag does not deploy in a collision
airbag light blinks on and off
driver or passenger injuries occur due to lack of airbag deployment.
